er values of T_0xH_0, the conclusions are the same\nregardless of whether any adjustments are made or not. The implications of\nthese results for cosmology and models of galaxy formation are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2001 08:21:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2001 08:27:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
